            "MediaUse": "Sigg Online",
            "AltText": "Photocopied collage on wood depicting eight orderly photocopies of a man’s face, divided into two rows, next to the words ‘Eight Bests’. The faces in the top row shows first a neutral expression, then smiling, then beaming, and then laughing. In the second row, the order is reversed. Each photocopy is accompanied by a remark concerning the movement of smile muscles and facial features.",
            "AltTextTC": "影印圖像木板拼貼。上面的八張影印整齊地分成兩行，全部顯示同一個男人的面孔，旁邊是「一個八拍」的字樣。頂行四張臉首先沒有表情，然後逐漸由微笑演變至張口大笑。第二行的面部表情次序相反，由大笑演變至木無表情。每張影印均附設註解，解釋如何活動笑肌和五官。",
